{"tid":1698351,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［突發］想發起不自殺聲明恆常化challenge","createTime":"2019-11-07T12:09:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-17T10:57:59.000Z","uid":180902,"like":74,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":41,"replies":[{"pid":"6653e848d5963ca993566011e2a80d89322a1311","tid":1698351,"uid":180902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T12:09:09.000Z","msg":"而家香港人不斷失蹤人人自危<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一個前一個鐘重同呀哥朋友有講有笑post 埋ig 既人<br />\n下一個鐘可以自殺死左<br />\n警方話無可疑<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n隨手一搵就一堆case<br />\n家樂旁公園發現屍體（慎入）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1698247\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1698247</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n可疑案件討論<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/jrC7FoUiZbk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FjrC7FoUiZbk&d=Z9XWEpuBYzNDjlwSEAyqK1tn4zyk5OLfN8GNswWzUNI%3D&h=06b41a96\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/jrC7FoUiZbk</a><br />\n<br />\n唔知你地咩感受 總之而家我見到警察好驚連個心都震埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我想發起不自殺聲明恆常化運動<br />\n大家每次係社交網ig fb講任何野都要加個tap   #不自殺聲明<br />\n每次見到有狗係視線可及範圍經過都要影相加tag #不自殺聲明<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\"><br />\n屌你老母我要見到成個ig個個post 所有香港人講親野都加句<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n#不自殺聲明<br />\n #如墬樓跳海必屬被殺<br />\n #到時無需理會真假家屬聲明請大家幫我尋冤得雪</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n好似太子站咁；擺花擺到行過唔關事既港豬都會問發生左咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />；外國人都會問做咩食飯飲水都要講明唔會自殺？？？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n上面既tag我要一search 幾十萬個result 搞撚大佢<br />\n<br />\n好處：<br />\n1. 和理非及勇武全民皆可參與<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n2. 零成本引起內外媒體關注<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n3. 當再有義士失蹤被自殺，而該義士曾重重復復貼過#不自殺聲明 ； 呢個就係最大証據； <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n4. 希望令每個義士都可以得到林林咁既關注；而關注需要証據；咁樣亦係保護其他義士唔再被跳樓既方法之一<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後p牌推唔到求大家幫幫忙推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋留個言講低點發大佢搞<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">保護義士從生活做起<br />\n五大訴求，決一不可</div></span></span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"da18785b4717bcbf049413fd2c3773ca7d957acf","tid":1698351,"uid":180902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T12:16:01.000Z","msg":"自己空氣推<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd7d5f5493fbf2936ce9523132b3dcd571c6e5f4","tid":1698351,"uid":230536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T12:17:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38d8b3986b916c54346700c9c9750641514b8fa9","tid":1698351,"uid":204625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T12:17:48.000Z","msg":"up"},{"pid":"a2f691bf833ddcef923f651fd0e9eb1c61ed68ed","tid":1698351,"uid":204835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T12:17:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ad1ee94ad78fe62a539e52f1e6f104d90a84eedf","tid":1698351,"uid":230536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T12:17:59.000Z","msg":"#不自殺聲明<br />\n#如墬樓跳海必屬被殺<br />\n#到時無需理會真假家屬聲明請大家幫我尋冤得"},{"pid":"b3c260cfe1c9f6645148827a200944dc061f43b7","tid":1698351,"uid":321977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T12:18:21.000Z","msg":"推，希望個個人fb ig都有不自殺聲明"},{"pid":"08e2045dcd8de985bd8b4fc80b61782d6d1efd12","tid":1698351,"uid":204835,"like":0,"disli