Z","msg":"唔係講笑。。。<br />\n寫張紙仔 覺得有危險就要俾人。。。<br />\n<br />\n將自己location 今日會去邊到玩講俾信得過既朋友知<br />\n<br />\ntelegram schdule msg要善用<br />\n<br />\n起碼俾到訊息 朋友 屋企人第一時間求援。。。<br />\n領事館。。。。"},{"pid":"f1c1ae4447e709ac6e29328ec58583a9bd9fa032","tid":1698351,"uid":82394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T12:29:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10cf95d10bf033139a12a5edd5b3f766ca352360","tid":1698351,"uid":180902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T12:30:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0PtK6rh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0PtK6rh.png&h=e0ec4901&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n#nonsuicidaldeclaration<br />\n#不自殺聲明"},{"pid":"977ff14b9b5bb02cc4b09f98e034743d9cba7d69","tid":1698351,"uid":180902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T12:33:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eFbkENn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeFbkENn.png&h=210b56e7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n吃得好飽哦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n#感到幸福<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n#nonsuicidaldeclaration<br />\n#不自殺聲明"},{"pid":"ee97b5e9022d93b51160071160c0606194046fae","tid":1698351,"uid":49898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T12:42:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e97f2f4d638cd6b34e5805a84b0c4bf48619a3a9","tid":1698351,"uid":180902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T12:47:03.000Z","msg":"邊個靜靜雞放負皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2bd1a51912fb30e4d455e0cab666996d7222cf6","tid":1698351,"uid":165749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T12:52:21.000Z","msg":"好難信唔係Popo做，講真，你估條街真係無popo? 由其是係旺區！！！！呢啲野俾啲所謂鄉黑既做一早黃左啦，殺完人，做野乾手淨腳既仲可以係咩人？"},{"pid":"70c9eca4442cf535d0714059443